thread.title: BRIEF-Euronext Implements A Liquidity Contract With Rothschild Martin Maurel

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Euronext Implements A Liquidity Contract With Rothschild Martin Maurel
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - Euronext Nv:
* EURONEXT NV - ANNOUNCES IMPLEMENTATION OF A LIQUIDITY CONTRACT WITH ROTHSCHILD MARTIN MAUREL
* EURONEXT NV - REQUESTED IMPLEMENTATION OF A ONE YEAR AND AUTOMATICALLY RENEWABLE LIQUIDITY CONTRACT WITH ROTHSCHILD MARTIN
* EURONEXT NV - CONTRACT WILL ALSO ABIDE BY COMMERCIAL CODE, AND DECISION TAKEN BY AMF ON MARCH 21(ST), 2011
* EURONEXT NV - AS OF 7 FEBRUARY 2018, LIQUIDITY CONTRACT WAS TERMINATED BY COMPANY EURONEXT N.V. WITH EXANE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
